Effects in tailwind

1-Add shadows, movement, and transformations when interacting with the element
<div class="shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition duration-300 p-4 bg-white">
  box
</div>


**note:**
shadow-{sm, md, lg, xl} → shadow

opacity-{0..100} → transparency

transition, duration-{ms} → Transition Movement

hover:, focus: → Impact when passing or focusing
